<br>
<br>
<br>
          Lady Persephoria,<br>
<br>
          It is with great pleasure I greet the news of your promotion within the Army.  I am sure, humble as you are, that you feel you have been honored greatly in this.  You have achieved a position of authority, responsibility, and respect within the most glorious institution the world shall ever know.<br>
<br>
          Our General has shown great confidence in you with her actions this day.  However, do not imagine that she has given this to you.  Although it is her will and wisdom which has allowed it, your advancement is nothing less than what you have earned.  It is the visible, physical manifestation of the faith which those who serve already have in you.  The courage, strength, and wisdom which you posess is a great boon to our cause.  Your spirit and selfless devotion continue to be a great inspiration.<br>
<br>
          Verily, it is the Army, and those of us who serve within it which are honored by your elevation.  By your merits alone have you risen to aid our General in leading us to victory.  We will not fail, for we are right.<br>
<br>
          The Malevolent banner shall be unfurled,<br>
          'twill fly across the sky.<br>
          In it's shadow shall fall the world;<br>
          beneath it light shall die.<br>
<br>
Hail Lady Persephoria, Officer of the Host!<br>
<br>
Hail Mistress Evani, General of the Army!<br>
<br>
The future is black, indeed!<br>
<br>
          With warmest regards,<br>
          Your humble servant,<br>
<br>
          Zathael. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoriafv>PersephoriaFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>~Magically Malicious~
